3. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper proposes a new algorithm for solving the rotation synchronization problem, which is a problem in data structures and algorithms. 
4. cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) - The proposed algorithm involves numerical optimization techniques, which fall under the category of numerical analysis.
